    <Note Title="Topic" Type="Summary" Ordinal="1" xml:lang="en">Security update for libssh</Note>
    <Note Title="Details" Type="General" Ordinal="2" xml:lang="en">libssh was updated to fix one security issue.

The following vulnerability was fixed:

* CVE-2015-3146: Specially crafted packages inserted into a connection could have lead to  a client or server process crash via a null pointer dereference.</Note>
